{"tid":1250554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見招拆招 理性分析 反黑警最佳部署","createTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:29:19.000Z","uid":37610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ad8923c536640ccc77adb04baa30691008cc0b","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"琴日真係俾D掌聲大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱到痾撚 我自己都差D 中暑<br />\n<br />\n總結就係G phone 呼籲包圍警總 要求同大狗哥對話之後遍地開花有其他人包圍其他政府大樓 ( 同幾年前 國民教育 政改 一樣 ）<br />\n<br />\n而政府回應 暫停 同 撤回 無分別 <br />\n警方 再不會清場 以逸待勞 忍住手腳 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地反送中 有成果 最大原因 <br />\n警察 濫用暴力 粗暴驅趕 示威者 <br />\n引起國際關注 逃犯條例<br />\n 並唔係我地包圍一個政府大樓 屌下老母 嗌下口號 可以做到 <br />\n簡單D 黎講 政府上次行錯棋 激起民憤 我地先有得贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地第一要 更加聚焦 包圍警總 就咪再嗌 撤回 <br />\n中政府伏 轉移視線 令廣大民眾 <br />\n以為年輕人係度恃住人多 <br />\n唔講道理執著字眼 得寸進尺 <br />\n<br />\n而家好明顯 我！ 地！ 香港人 ！<br />\n係要追究警權過大問題 反黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n投訴無門 <br />\n逍遙法外 <br />\n黑警可恥<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議 <br />\n一人一封投訴信 <br />\n明確訴求 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家試諗下 幾萬封甚至過百萬封信 放係邊到 都係何其壯觀 <br />\n當然 大家附件 可以唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞蛋啊 毅進宣傳單張啊 狗仔圖 長輩圖啊 <br />\n到時大家識做啦（其他不合作運動可以繼續做）<br />\n<br />\n依個方法 最起碼 <br />\n<br />\n逼政府警方正面回應 <br />\nCCTVB正面報導 <br />\n媒體廣泛報導<br />\n國際頭版指日可待 <br />\n<br />\n拆解依家 逃犯條例字眼漩渦 <br />\n無可否認 反送中已經有成果 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反黑警係停滯不前</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知道要大家接受 暫停 好難 <br />\n只不過大家要知道<br />\n兵無常勢，水無常形；<br />\n能因敵變化而取勝，謂之神<br />\n唔好唔記得係邊個打到我地爆唒缸 咳到肺痛 <br />\n<br />\n我地都唔想見到<br />\n政府 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">棄車保狗</span></span> 奸計得逞<br />\n係咪先！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人！ <br />\n拎我地最強既武器<br />\n投訴之刀  <br />\n一野劈落去班狗到</span></span>"},{"pid":"193a4b4bc79c2af1d78c2b52aec823a91d8aa926","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c66f09a8ab04ee76776c671e2a847df10569ba3f","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93aa5f46beced5293749b91cba79b6721568dc6","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b60a7cc5addc8f488b081f386c50b7dea9bacdd2","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5eb71ddadce564fc4497ed75e40cb7d6c0d5d2","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"f10a1d239bd12610408f8d1873320e8bb3654b83","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42fe8fc11e934fd6d649ccbe4eb36ae3a1669df0","tid":1250554,"uid":37610,"like":0,"disl